                     <handNote xml:id="h4" script="Ethiopic">
Hand c: fols. 45va-46vb (Text IV). It is difficult to determine whether one or more scribes were involved in writing. Probably the text was written in one hand at several stages. <!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h5" script="Ethiopic">
